    "body": "Managed to capture two CPU profiles at start and at a higher value:\r\n\r\n- Profile 1: 1653974851, Tue May 31 2022 05:27:31 GMT+0000 [CPU-hetzner-ropsten-3-validator-1653974851.zip](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/8825408/CPU-hetzner-ropsten-3-validator-1653974851.zip) CPU usage rate = 2%\r\n- Profile 2: 1654183940, Thu Jun 02 2022 15:32:20 GMT+0000 [CPU-hetzner-ropsten-3-validator-1654183940.zip](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/8825407/CPU-hetzner-ropsten-3-validator-1654183940.zip) CPU usage rate = 6% \r\n\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-06-02 22-43-01](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/171668550-3dee24f3-65c7-44cd-8ef9-67ee3a2f0b0f.png)\r\n\r\n**Profile 1 Heavy (bottom-up) (CPU 2%)**\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-06-02 22-47-09](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/171669777-da1c877d-6dee-44c5-bcd5-87cd080298b4.png)\r\n\r\n**Profile 2 Heavy (bottom-up) (CPU 6%)**\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-06-02 22-47-37](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/171669896-c04bee95-a73a-4f91-9e55-5d5f9437a25f.png)\r\n\r\n**Heap-snapshot 1 (CPU 2%)**\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-06-02 22-53-59](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/171672238-bda01a32-b3ac-4d1b-8e6c-507a635465cd.png)\r\n\r\n**Heap-snapshot 2 (CPU 6%)**\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2022-06-02 23-08-03](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/171675169-578016f1-51cb-4635-9ae4-c19b80bb5c9b.png)\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nSo this most likely looks like a leak and improper handling of signals in the lodestar-api client request function.\r\n- CPU increase caused by EventTarget adding and removing listeners\r\n- Memory increase caused by many EventTarget and AbortController (78,000).\r\n",
