    "body": "Looks like the leak is caused here, where the callback being un-subscribed is not the same as the one being subscribed\r\n\r\nAdds `() => controller.abort()`, removes `controller.abort`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/86b95a731d8d9443580a66707bc30a722f387941/packages/api/src/client/utils/httpClient.ts#L85\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/86b95a731d8d9443580a66707bc30a722f387941/packages/api/src/client/utils/httpClient.ts#L133",
